---
/**
 * EC²R brand text with tight kerning on the superscript 2.
 * The Unicode ² has wider metrics, making it look detached from C and R.
 * Usage: <EC2R /> renders inline EC²R with proper spacing.
 */
---
<Fragment>EC<sup style="font-size:0.65em;margin:0 -0.07em;vertical-align:super">2</sup>R</Fragment>
